{"tid":2321961,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港電台：美國最高法院駁回得州尋求推翻大選結果的訴訟","createTime":"2020-12-12T02:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T03:15:37.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d61bf049ed36d823f08b28bc82123b34437c01a","tid":2321961,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564920-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564920-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmrTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=f270673a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564920-20201212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a8f4a674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564920-20201212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n美國最高法院駁回得州提出尋求推翻大選結果的訴訟請求。<br />\n<br />\n得州今個星期較早時提出訴訟，試圖推翻佐治亞州、密歇根州、賓夕法尼亞州和威斯康星州的選舉結果，這4個州都由民主黨拜登勝出。訴訟得到19個州的檢察長，及127名共和黨國會議員支持，總統特朗普日前亦表明支持訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n不過最高法院裁定，<strong>得州在其他州的選舉問題上，並沒有司法上可識別的權益，駁回訴訟。<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"34d2b4674d7c6bd8df400cb1eae8273e3061676a","tid":2321961,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"係係係，全世界都幫拜登"}]}